OL,6,FCultural change at the crisis-hit
OL,7,FSouth Wales Fire is underway but it
OL,8,Fwill be "a marathon, not a sprint",
OL,9,Faccording to the service's new chief.
OL,11,FFin Monahan says the last year has
OL,12,F"dented the morale" of his staff and
OL,13,Fhe acknowledges the magnitude of the
OL,14,Fchallenge he has turning things around.
