OL,3,CFire boss admits morale is low but
OL,4,Cvows to deliver real change
OL,6,FThe service has faced a turbulent year
OL,7,Fafter the publication of a report
OL,8,Fwhich found bullying, sexism and
OL,9,Fracism went unchallenged. The
OL,10,Fappointment of a controversial interim
OL,11,Fchief caused further issues for the
OL,12,Fservice, with staff telling ITV it
OL,13,F"did nothing to reassure staff".
OL,15,FHowever, the new boss insisted he had
OL,16,F"come in with the express job of
OL,17,Fcompletely changing the culture."
