OL,3,CFire boss admits morale is low but
OL,4,Cvows to deliver real change
OL,6,FUntil recently Fin Monahan was a
OL,7,Fcommander in the RAF, but last week he
OL,8,Ftook up the top job at the crisis-hit
OL,9,FSouth Wales Fire and Rescue Service.
OL,11,FIn January, a damning review of the
OL,12,Fculture there was published and
OL,13,Fexposed how sexism, misogyny and
OL,14,Fracism were tolerated among staff.
OL,16,FFenella Morris KC's report made 82
OL,17,Frecommendations and the chief then,
OL,18,FHuw Jakeway, announced he would stand
OL,19,Fdown.
