OL,3,CFire boss admits morale is low but
OL,4,Cvows to deliver real change
OL,6,FStuart Millington was brought in as
OL,7,Fthe interim chief fire officer while
OL,8,Fthe South Wales service found a new
OL,9,Fboss. However, ITV revealed that Mr
OL,10,FMillington was, himself, at the centre
OL,11,Fof bullying allegations. Unions
OL,12,Fdescribed his appointment as
OL,13,F"shocking".
OL,15,FAn employment court has since struck
OL,16,Fout the case against Mr Millington
OL,17,Fafter it was argued the claimant
OL,18,Fsubmitted his complaint outside of the
OL,19,Flegal time limit. Mr Millington always
OL,20,Fdenied the allegations and faces no
OL,21,Ffurther action.
