OL,3,CFire boss admits morale is low but
OL,4,Cvows to deliver real change
OL,6,FIn August, staff described how a
OL,7,Fturbulent 8 months had significantly
OL,8,Fimpacted morale at the service. One
OL,9,Ftold us that morale at the service had
OL,10,F"never been lower".
OL,12,FLow morale is a big concern for the
OL,13,Fnew chief. Air Vice Marshall Monahan
OL,14,Fsaid he has spent the last week
OL,15,Fspeaking to staff and thinks "morale
OL,16,Fis very very dented".
