OL,3,CFire boss admits morale is low but
OL,4,Cvows to deliver real change
OL,6,F"Going out on the ground,
OL,7,F(firefighter's) morale is extremely
OL,8,Fdented. And it is my job to get their
OL,9,Fmorale back up make sure that everyone
OL,10,Fis safe, so that we deliver a very
OL,11,Feffective 24/7 response," he said.
OL,13,FThe new chief says he has the
OL,14,Fexperience needed to transform the
OL,15,Fservice: "I protect people, that's
OL,16,Fwhat I do", he said. The former Red
OL,17,FArrows commander has written papers on
OL,18,Ftransforming organisational change and
OL,19,Fhas overseen a change in the military.
