OL,3,CFire boss admits morale is low but
OL,4,Cvows to deliver real change
OL,6,FHowever, Fin Monahan says he
OL,7,Funderstands the size of the change
OL,8,Fneeded. "This is big", he told us,
OL,9,F"We're about to carry out, what I
OL,10,Fthink is, the most fundamental culture
OL,11,Fchange programme that the public
OL,12,Fservice has ever seen."
OL,14,FThe North and Mid & West Wales fire
OL,15,Fservices have also found themselves
OL,16,Funder the spotlight for cultural
OL,17,Fissues this year. In June, a Senedd
OL,18,Freport said that fire chiefs across
OL,19,FWales had not come to terms with the
OL,20,Fscale of the cultural issues they face.
