OL,3,CFire boss admits morale is low but
OL,4,Cvows to deliver real change
OL,6,FThe new chief of the South Wales
OL,7,Fservice insisted he is not in denial
OL,8,Fabout the change needed. "This is an
OL,9,Forganisation that for about two years
OL,10,Fhas been in the public eye with a
OL,11,Fculture problem.
OL,13,F"The people of my organisation are
OL,14,Fvery clear that there is a problem,
OL,15,FI'm very clear there is a problem -
OL,16,Fthat's why I have been recruited", he
OL,17,Fsaid.
