OL,3,CFire boss admits morale is low but
OL,4,Cvows to deliver real change
OL,6,FHowever, some inside his service have
OL,7,Ftold us they are waiting to be
OL,8,Fconvinced by their new boss. Staff
OL,9,Fhave said to us they have waited more
OL,10,Fthan 8 months without any change.
OL,12,FAfter almost a year of scandal at the
OL,13,Fservice, firefighters we have spoken
OL,14,Fto say their new chief has an uphill
OL,15,Fbattle to convince staff that change
OL,16,Fis coming.
